title: #306: Mother Fucker (@ChristinaP)
itunes:title: Mother F*cker with Christina P
description: Christina Pazsitzky met me in LA to talk about motherhood. She just became a mom a couple years ago. It's the first realistic version of motherhood that i've ever heard. Good into and outro, too.
